'''2015年蓋提夫清真寺爆炸案'''，是指發生於2015年5月22日，於[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]][[東部省|東部省]][[蓋提夫|蓋提夫]]市的[[自殺攻擊|自殺攻擊]]爆炸案<ref name="林育菱">{{cite news|author1=林育菱|title=沙國清真寺爆炸案21死百傷 伊斯蘭國認了|url=http://www.storm.mg/article/50468|accessdate=2015-05-23|agency=[[風傳媒|風傳媒]]|date=2015-05-23|archive-date=2015-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525144044/http://www.storm.mg/article/50468|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名自殺炸彈客衝入了艾卡迪村（al-Qadeeh）阿里教長（Imam Ali）[[清真寺|清真寺]]引爆炸彈。當時正在舉行禮拜儀式，有超過150人在寺內祈禱，導致至少21人死亡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentid=20150523244748 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524173638/http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentid=20150523244748 |archivedate=2015-05-24 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/news/750821 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-23 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012073804/http://www.arabnews.com/saudi-arabia/news/750821 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/saudi-arabia-shia-mosque-attack-150522101243243.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-23 |archive-date=2017-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111202424/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/saudi-arabia-shia-mosque-attack-150522101243243.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。案發後，[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]已聲稱為本起爆炸案的主謀<ref name="林育菱" /><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/saudi-shia-mosque-suicide-bomb-150522101-150522131614062.html | title=ISIL claims responsibility for Saudi mosque attack | publisher=Al-Jazeera | accessdate=23 May 2015 | archive-date=2017-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107021735/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/05/saudi-shia-mosque-suicide-bomb-150522101-150522131614062.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
{{seealso|沙烏地阿拉伯什葉派}}
據統計，在[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]的{{link-en|沙烏地阿拉伯什葉派|Shia Islam in Saudi Arabia|什葉派穆斯林}}約占該國[[公民|公民]]總數的14%至15%，其餘為[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]<ref>{{cite web|title=沙烏地阿拉伯國家概況|url=http://big5.chinanews.com:89/gj/zlk/2014/01-15/195.shtml|publisher=[[中國新聞網|中國新聞網]]|accessdate=2015-05-23|date=2013-11|quote=【人 口】2838萬(2013年)，其中沙特公民約佔70%。伊斯蘭教為國教，遜尼派佔85%，什葉派佔15%。|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140731104431/http://big5.chinanews.com:89/gj/zlk/2014/01-15/195.shtml|archivedate=2014-07-31}}</ref>。這些什葉派穆斯林主要居住在沙國石油豐富的東部地區，而在沙國佔主導地位的則是[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]的支派[[瓦哈比派|瓦哈比派]]。瓦哈比派掌控了國家的[[教育|教育]]、[[法院|法院]]、[[宗教|宗教]]等機構，認為什葉派不是真正的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，因此在該國的什葉派穆斯林受到嚴重歧視<ref name=holymen>{{cite book|last=Commins |first=David |title=The Wahhabi Mission and Saudi Arabia |publisher=I.B.Tauris |year=2009 |pages=155–6|quote=Muhammad ibn Abd al-Wahhab ... insisted that invoking and making vows to holy men indeed constituted major idolatry and that it was proper to deem as infidels anyone who failed to view such practices as idolatry.  ... He then stated that if one admits that these practices are major idolatry, then fighting is a duty as part of the prophetic mission to destroy idols. Thus, the idolater who call upon a saint for help must repent, If he does so, his repentance is accepted. If not, he is to be killed. }}</ref><ref name=ibnghannam>{{cite book|last=Ibn Ghannam |first=Hussien |title=Tarikh najd |location=Cairo |year=1961 |page=438}}</ref>。

根據[[人权观察|人权观察]]組織在2009年的報告，在沙國的什葉派穆斯林於教育、司法、宗教，甚至於就業各方面都承受著長期與系統性的歧視。雖然同屬[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]，但什葉派穆斯林被瓦哈比派視為[[異教徒|異教徒]]或[[無神論|無神論]]者，尤其在教育與司法的歧視最為嚴重，什葉派穆斯林被禁止參軍、擔任警察等職務，甚至連出庭[[證人|作證]]也不允許<ref name=謝雯伃>{{cite news|title=沙國什葉派穆斯林飽受歧視|author1=謝雯伃|url=http://www.lihpao.com/?action-viewnews-itemid-21761|accessdate=2015-05-23|agency=[[亞洲新聞|亞洲新聞]]|publisher=[[台灣立報|台灣立報]]|date=2009-09-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524023418/http://www.lihpao.com/?action-viewnews-itemid-21761|archivedate=2015-05-24}}</ref>。

2011年起的[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]，結果壯大了[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]。其後，沙國也開始介入了[[也门内战_(2014年至今)|葉門內戰]]。2014年11月的[[阿舒拉节|阿舒拉节]]，有8名什葉派穆斯林在[[哈薩綠洲|哈薩綠洲]]遭到槍擊身亡，蓋提夫市議員兼人權活動者Jafar Al Shayeb在當時即已預測，之後沙國什葉派與遜尼派的衝突將會更趨劇烈；他認為在[[萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特|萨勒曼王]]針對什葉派[[胡塞武裝組織|胡塞武裝組織]]的[[果斷風暴行動|一連串攻擊行動]]後，也使得沙國內部什葉派的處境更加惡化<ref>{{cite news|title=Saudi suicide bombing: Shi'ite stronghold Qatif was a Sunni terrorist target waiting to happen|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/saudi-suicide-bombing-shia-stronghold-qatif-was-sunni-terrorist-target-waiting-happen-1502546|accessdate=23 May 2015|publisher=IB Times|date=23 May 2015|archive-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620024515/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/saudi-suicide-bombing-shia-stronghold-qatif-was-sunni-terrorist-target-waiting-happen-1502546|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一位在[[倫敦|倫敦]]的什葉派批評者認為，雖然近幾年沙國政府對於什葉派的歧視略有減弱，但瓦巴比派的沙國王室，基本上與伊斯蘭國領導者的心態沒有什麼兩樣，甚至在某些教條也有相似之處，所以沙國政府一直沒有對國內兩個教派間的緊張關係，做出有效解決。迄今在沙烏地阿拉伯的遜尼派神職人員，若宣傳反什葉派的說詞，仍不會受到任何懲罰或[[逮捕|逮捕]]。例如在爆炸案發生前的幾個小時，[[利雅德|利雅德]]的神職人員在宣教時就曾稱，要[[安拉|安拉]]殺死所有的什葉派<ref>{{cite news|title=Bloodshed in the kingdom|url=http://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21652037-rare-bomb-hits-shia-mosque-bloodshed-kingdom|accessdate=23 May 2015|publisher=Economist|date=23 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524022407/http://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21652037-rare-bomb-hits-shia-mosque-bloodshed-kingdom|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 爆炸 ==
根據[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]]的報導，有大約150人出席了在當地[[清真寺|清真寺]]周五例行的[[主麻日|主麻日]]祈禱。一位目擊者聲稱，至少有30人被炸死<ref>{{cite web |author= Suman Varandani |url= http://www.ibtimes.com/saudi-arabia-suicide-bombing-shiite-mosque-attacked-during-friday-prayers-casualties-1934453 |title= Saudi Arabia Suicide Bombing: Shiite Mosque Attacked During Friday Prayers, Casualties Reported |publisher= International Business Times |date= May 22, 2015 |accessdate= May 22, 2015 |archive-date= 2015-05-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150522180536/http://www.ibtimes.com/saudi-arabia-suicide-bombing-shiite-mosque-attacked-during-friday-prayers-casualties-1934453 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。本起自殺炸彈攻擊的結果，還導致50餘人受傷，這也是首起在沙烏地阿拉伯發生的清真寺主麻日期間自殺攻擊案<ref>{{cite web |author= ABDULLAH AL-SHIHRI and AYA BATRAWY |url= http://bigstory.ap.org/article/76d48760d33748769bd3d067ac0a17fc/suicide-bomber-targets-shiite-worshippers-saudi-arabia |title= Suicide bomber targets Shiite worshippers in Saudi Arabia |publisher= A P |date= May 22, 2015 |accessdate= May 22, 2015 |archive-date= 2015-05-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150522173332/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/76d48760d33748769bd3d067ac0a17fc/suicide-bomber-targets-shiite-worshippers-saudi-arabia |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=reuters>{{cite web|author= SAMI ABOUDI|url= http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/22/us-saudi-security-idUSKBN0O712S20150522|title= Suicide bomber strikes Saudi Shi'ite mosque, many dead or wounded: residents|publisher= Reuters|date= May 22, 2015|accessdate= May 22, 2015|archive-date= 2015-05-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150522220217/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/22/us-saudi-security-idUSKBN0O712S20150522|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://rt.com/news/261141-bomber-saudi-arabia-prayers/|title=30 casualties feared in suicide bomber attack on mosque in S. Arabia (GRAPHIC IMAGES)|work=rt.com|accessdate=22 May 2015|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222210446/https://www.rt.com/news/261141-bomber-saudi-arabia-prayers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

